<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Faculty</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to external CSS file -->
    <style>
        /* Internal CSS styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        section {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .faculty-member {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .faculty-member:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        .faculty-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        .faculty-description {
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>About Our Faculty</h1>
</header>

<section>
    <div class="faculty-member">
        <h2 class="faculty-name">Dr. John Doe</h2>
        <p class="faculty-description">Dr. John Doe is a Professor of Computer Science at XYZ University. He specializes in artificial intelligence and machine learning.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faculty-member">
        <h2 class="faculty-name">Prof. Jane Smith</h2>
        <p class="faculty-description">Prof. Jane Smith is an Associate Professor of Mathematics at XYZ University. She conducts research in mathematical modeling and optimization.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faculty-member">
        <h2 class="faculty-name">Dr. Michael Johnson</h2>
        <p class="faculty-description">Dr. Michael Johnson is an Assistant Professor of Biology at XYZ University. His research interests include ecology and conservation biology.</p>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
